Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy
of this software and associated documentation files (the “Software”), to deal
in the Software without restriction, including without limitation the rights
to use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and/or sell
copies of the Software, subject to the following conditions:

1. If the Software is used in a product or service with more than 500,000
   monthly active users, the licensee must pay the Licensor a revenue share
   starting at 1% of the gross revenue derived from the Software or its
   related services, payable quarterly.

2. Each time the number of monthly active users doubles beyond 500,000, the
   revenue share rate shall be reduced to two-thirds (⅔) of the previous rate.
   For example:
      • ≥ 500,000 users: 1%
      • ≥ 1,000,000 users: 0.666…%
      • ≥ 2,000,000 users: 0.444…%
      • ≥ 4,000,000 users: 0.296…%
      • and so on.

3. “Monthly active users” means unique users who access the product or service
   in any rolling 30-day period.

4. This payment obligation does not apply to non-commercial use.

5. The above copyright notice and this permission notice shall be included in
   all copies or substantial portions of the Software.

